{"tid":504698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"模擬核電廠洩漏 大亞灣應變計劃跨部門演習今起舉行","createTime":"2017-12-20T09:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T12:13:40.000Z","uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b809a7153389143d0eaaa6a21f7dfee5055c6e6f","tid":504698,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57603260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57603260&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=6a49399e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57603260&h=8355b132\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57603260</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174512_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174512_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=66dd8905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174521_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174521_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bdafb5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174532_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174532_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ffdf8698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日政府進行為期兩天的大亞灣應變計劃跨部門演習，目標是測試及提升政府應對可能影響香港的嚴重核事故能力、測試大亞灣應變計劃效能等。該大型演習每隔3至5年才舉行一次，對上一次演習已是2012年4月舉行。<br />\n<br />\n今次代號「棋盤二」的演習，政府邀請法國輻射防護與核安全研究院擔任顧問，主要模擬大亞灣核電站發生嚴重輻射事故，通過桌面演練及實地演習，全面測試政府應急能力。演習重點測試範疇包括事故通報和訊息交換、後果監測及評估、政府應變架構的啟動、煙羽防護措施、飲食防護措施、向公眾提供協助及發布公眾資訊。<br />\n<br />\n今次演習會有30多個合共超過3,000人與應變計劃有關的決策局、部門及機構參與，包括保安局、食衞局、環境局、警隊、消防處、香港天文台、醫管局等，針對模擬核事故採取相應行動並互動配合，以展示其應付緊急情況的判斷力、效率及專業知識，演習將包括特定的實地行動，以測試前線部門的執行和協調能力。<br />\n<br />\n在首日的演習中，會模擬大亞灣核電廠發生洩漏，政府根據國際規定，疏散大亞灣核電廠20公哩範圍內的市民，而本港只有東坪洲在此範圍內，故首日演習以東坪洲為起點，島上數十名居民中，部分居民會參與演習，模擬疏散到馬料水水警基地，然後接受政府人員的核輻射檢測及相關跟進工作，另水務署亦會到水塘模擬檢測食水是否受輻射污染。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當局檢討2012年演習經驗，在今次演習會作出一些改善措施，包括在東坪洲發出疏散廣播，除繼續使用直升機廣播外，亦會使用島上設立的廣播器及水警輪發布訊息；放棄找學生參與演習，「因為上次搵學生扮災民，但部分人演習期間食薯片等小食，好似去野餐，被外界批評演習兒戲，所以今次就唔搵佢哋，只係搵東坪洲居民參與」。<br />\n<br />\n另政府今次邀請國際、內地及香港專家和政府代表觀察演習，亦會邀請立法會保安事務委員會委員觀察。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超下午視察完演習後會見傳媒，指政府模擬上午接獲核事故通報後，啟動大亞灣應變計劃，行政長官督導小組模擬因應事故召開會議，商討由保安局局長率領的大亞灣應變計劃執行小組提出的建議，而大部份措施在上午的演習中均有執行。他指明天第二日演習會移師東區醫院，模擬處理核事故傷者，另亦會移師文錦渡，模擬監進口的食物及禽畜有否受到核污染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174357_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174357_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=381a7e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=04179d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/174454_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F174454_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d5590f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513c70b4494aae24ce41f8ef146222df837f5bc0","tid":504698,"uid":69971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7539294451290dad3df5e2f7fb75af3517793e","tid":504698,"uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"20公里本身已經夠晒兒戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過一到30公里疏散範圍人口多好多，政府根本唔想搞，象徵性要東坪洲班人走咪算當做左野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd159133863b869c2ecc3f7b600f60e16b471d4c","tid":504698,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁就當做咗野？"},{"pid":"c95a0975216fbc8cb1793aa816059c4fd0ae285f","tid":504698,"uid":163399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4873fcba1b4f3cdfaf21d03a40913eac6835df67","tid":504698,"uid":163399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92dd863c88386dd53dd9c665171863db788c9874","tid":504698,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"將來核戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d411b7445b380448fe27e71eb619554616dfec","tid":504698,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"話就話模擬<br />\n其實實戰黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0971f88cce0336cce9e51ab49d49d6079d891c3f","tid":504698,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"總有一天需要嘅"}]}